    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Use with reference to abstract paintings of the 1960s and 1970s that repeat or vary a motif from work to work or within a work.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
